Items.mt: Haha, who do you think I am? The first thing I knew about you was that you were investigating things in Xiaoxi Village, pursuing a corruption case against the governor of Kaifeng, fighting against the Manichaean church of Zhao Li, not that far-flung, illusory princess of the Song Dynasty.
